Lolly Ink is bummed that her boyfriend is working late and can't take her out. Her friend, Tasha, invites Lolly to join her and her boyfriend, Johnny, on a night out. Lolly is reluctant to join at first as she does not want to be the third wheel, but she goes along after some convincing from Tasha. When they get home from their night out Tasha invites Lolly to join her and her man in bed for a hot threesome and Lolly gladly joins.
